mixin Faq
	+Section('container-small').pt-9.pt-sm-14
		.row.flex-center
			.col-12.col-xl-7
				h2.text-center.mb-6.mb-sm-10 Frequently asked questions
				.accordion
					.accordion-item.border-top.border-200
						h2#headingOne.accordion-header
							button.accordion-button.fs-1.pb-3(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#collapseOne', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapseOne')
								| What about the update procedure of the theme?
						#collapseOne.accordion-collapse.collapse.show(aria-labelledby='headingOne', data-bs-parent='#accordionExample')
							.accordion-body.pt-0
								| This is our newest admin dashboard. We'll keep updating it according to users' needs. We keep a changelog with every release, so you'll be able to update the theme from one version to another with that changelog.
					.accordion-item
						h2#headingTwo.accordion-header
							button.accordion-button.fs-1.pb-3.collapsed(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#collapseTwo', aria-expanded='true', aria-controls='collapseOne')
								| Is there any Trial version of Phoenix?
						#collapseTwo.accordion-collapse.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingTwo', data-bs-parent='#accordionExample')
							.accordion-body.pt-0
								| We are sorry to inform you that there is no free or trial version of Phoenix, but you would get a full refund within 10 days if the template does not match your requirement.
					.accordion-item
						h2#headingThree.accordion-header
							button.accordion-button.fs-1.pb-3.collapsed(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#collapseThree', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapseOne')
								| Is it possible to build a mobile app using Phoenix components?
						#collapseThree.accordion-collapse.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingThree', data-bs-parent='#accordionExample')
							.accordion-body.pt-0
